	<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><FONT size=5>昆山开发区、昆山高新区、花桥经济开发区管委会，各镇人民政府：<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><FONT size=5>根据江苏省经信委《关于开展<SPAN lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN>年两化融合网络信息安全试点示范的通知》（苏经信信安〔<SPAN lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN>〕<SPAN lang=EN-US>657</SPAN>号）要求，<SPAN style="COLOR: black">现在我市开展<SPAN lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN>年两化融合网络信息安全试点示范申报工作。具体事项通知如下：<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; COLOR: #333333; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><FONT size=5>一、试点申报<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=1><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、申报条件：原则上为国家或省级两化融合管理体系贯标试点企业；具有一定的行业典型性，两化融合程度较高；试点工作需围绕在用的工控系统和网络信息系统展开；优先考虑先进制造、钢铁、有色、化工、石油石化、烟草等重点领域工业企业。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=1><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、申报材料：按要求填写提交《江苏省两化融合网络信息安全试点企业申报表》（附件<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>）及《江苏省两化融合网络信息安全试点工作方案》（附件<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>）。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; COLOR: #333333; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><FONT size=5>二、示范申报<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">、申报条件：是省两化融合网络信息安全管理试点企业且试点工作验收合格，或是已建立健全网络信息安全管理制度体系和工作机制，且运行良好的国家或省级两化融合贯标企业；按照《工业企业网络信息安全管理的指导意见》要求，严格落实工业企业网络信息安全责任制，建立健全各项管理机制和技术保障措施；定期开展网络信息系统（含工控系统）安全风险评估，根据风险评估情况采取措施进行相应整改加固，确保《工业控制系统信息安全防护指南》、《工业控制系统信息安全事件应急管理工作指南》等规范标准落实到位；近三年未发生重大网络信息安全事件。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">、申报材料：按要求填写提交《江苏省两化融合网络信息安全示范企业申报表》（附件<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>）、重要信息系统（含工控系统）信息安全风险评估报告。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; COLOR: #333333; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><FONT size=5>三、其他要求<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">请各申报单位填写申报材料。试点企业纸质申报材料</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">（一式两份）</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">于</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>9</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>28</SPAN>日前报市经信委软件和信息化推进科</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">，电子版申报材料发送至指定邮箱。示范企业纸质申报材料</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">（一式两份）</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">和电子版申报材料于<SPAN lang=EN-US>11</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>28</SPAN>日前报</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">市经信委软件和信息化推进科</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">联系人：马步青，邮箱：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>mbq717</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: #333333; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>@</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>163.com</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，联系电话：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>0512-57017933 </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，通讯地址：昆山市祖冲之南路</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1666</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">号清华科技园科技大厦</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">楼</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>402</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">室，邮编：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>215300</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">特此通知。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=5></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.45pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">附件：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋">、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">江苏省两化融合网络信息安全试点企业申报表</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.45pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </SPAN>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋">、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">江苏省两化融合网络信息安全试点工作方案</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
